{"tid":1834083,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有還押左64日既手足可以番屋企過年！！！","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T10:47:12.000Z","uid":8807,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6588e91e8aae05d98b9bda83081f408bfaf6802","tid":1834083,"uid":8807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:48:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">#屯門裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n水佳麗裁判官<br />\n<br />\n梁🛑已還押64天<br />\n<br />\n控罪：暴動<br />\n<br />\n案情：於 11 月 18 日於在九龍油麻地彌敦道近窩打老道交界參加暴動。<br />\n<br />\n早前向潘敏琦法官申請保釋被拒。今日，水佳麗裁判官准予被控人保釋<br />\n<br />\n保釋條件如下：<br />\n。$5000擔保金<br />\n。宵禁：2000至0630<br />\n。不得離港<br />\n。交出旅遊證件<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但若有再犯，法庭並不會再次批准保釋<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n因為要讀書連報到都唔洗重可以5000保釋真係第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>還押左64日</strong>終於可以番屋企過年<br />\n潘熙資深大狀真係好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫左民陣律師團啲手足好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f76dae2d8f60256c97e55600b82863425c05b0","tid":1834083,"uid":8807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"910adfb94f1edc73c44d6b93116cad8536bc858c","tid":1834083,"uid":343361,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好覺得係恩尉<br />\n根本無辜座咁耐<br />\n追討返兩個月薪金都好"},{"pid":"39feda109427cb31d230884bd7b003677ea8f30d","tid":1834083,"uid":29381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:51:26.000Z","msg":"潘律師 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7662221858874327a18816d134a241fe8e4b7d5e","tid":1834083,"uid":8807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"910adfb94f1edc73c44d6b93116cad8536bc858c","tid":1834